data.description: Small Town Living! Check out this 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom home which offers a formal dining room, large family room, and a living room which are all conveniently located on 1 level. The home is situated on a large fenced-in lot and features an oversized 1 car garage with convenient alley access and an exterior cellar entrance. Home is being sold As-Is. Call for a showing today!
